room_title: Escape room "The Test" by MacGyver's Great Escape in Florence (KY)
room_description: Guess what? It's test time, and you forgot to study! This is the big test that decides if you will spend your summer in school. The teachers will be arriving in one hour! You need to break into the classroom, find the test, and get out without a trace! Can you succeed or will you sentence yourself to a summer of boredom?
